"pln\">\r\n    </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> index </span><span class=\"pun\">==</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"lit\">1</span><span class=\"pun\">){</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n        value</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">html</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'hoge\'</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n        console</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">log</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">index</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> value</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n    </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"pun\">});</span></code></pre>\r\n<p>Kết quả:<br><img src=\"https://rongvangit.com/storage/1/uuiGQI0fqDVMS1i2XRXBNU2vchl1aEBz8Ob6GVYW.png\" alt=\"lay-phan-tu-tu-class-trong-jquerry2.png\"></p>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2-to-n-b-m-l-nh\"><a name=\"Toàn bộ mã lệnh\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>Toàn bộ mã lệnh</h2><pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code class=\"lang-html\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;script</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">src</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">integrity</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"sha256-/xUj+3OJU5yExlq6GSYGSHk7tPXikynS7ogEvDej/m4=\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">crossorigin</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;div</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">class</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span