span class=\"pln\"> $week</span><span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"pln\">$w</span><span class=\"pun\">];</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"kwd\">print</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">$day_of_week</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> \r\n\r\n</span><span class=\"com\">//Tuesday</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></code></pre>\r\n<p>Lại nữa, bằng cách thay đổi giá trị của mảng week, chúng ta cũng có thể <strong>lấy thứ bằng tiếng Việt trong PHP</strong> như sau:</p>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code class=\"lang-php\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php\r\n$datetime </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">new</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"typ\">DateTime</span><span class=\"pun\">();</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n$week </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> array</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\"CN\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"T2\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"T3\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"T4\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"T5\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"T6\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"T7\"</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n$w </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\">$datetime</span><span class=\"pun\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">format</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'w\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span cla